                                <div class="backTitle">The pros and cons of mandatory military service.</div>
                                <div class = "backBody">
                                    <div class = "backSourceName">Article written by Unknown</div>
                                    <div class="backBodyText">
                                        
                                        <!-- <img src = "public/images/happinessMap.png" style = "width: 300px" /> -->
                                        <h2>The pros<span class = "sitedSource"><sup>[6]</sup></span>:</h2>
                                        <p>            
                                            <ol>
                                                <li>Promotes National Unity</li>
                                                <li>Maintain Active Military Force</li>
                                                <li>Ensures High Levels of Governmental Participation</li>
                                                <li>Can Provide Useful Skills</li>
                                                <li>Promote Equality Among Citizens</li>
                                            </ol>                                    
                                        </p>
                                        <h2>The Cons<span class = "sitedSource"><sup>[6]</sup></span>:</h2>
                                        <p>
                                            <ol>
                                                <li>Violates Free Will</li>
                                                <li>Interferes with Other Forms of Education</li>
                                                <li>Put Young People’s Lives at Risk</li>
                                                <li>Compromises the Quality of Military Service</li>
                                                <li>Not Everyone Is Fit for It</li>
                                            </ol>     
                                        </p>
                                        <h2>My thoughts:</h2>
                                        <p>
                                            I think that while having a full militia of young and able people would be nice, allowing all children the chance to develop and reach adulthood is more important. As can be seen in figure 1, countries that enforce mandatory conscription, on average, have a lower quality of life (figure 2).
                                            The other fundamental issue with forcing people to enroll in the military that I can't ignore is the violation of basic rights of freedom. 
                                        </p>
                                        <p>
                                            However, I think there are times when conscription could be considered acceptable. Most people, I would say, value having general freedom over tyrany and wars sometimes need to be fought to protect those freedoms. If the military is too small, then the nation will fall to the hands of whoever has the 
                                            largest army. In cases when national security is directly threatened, I think that conscription could be allowed and celebrated, as a method of repaying our country for all of the freedoms it gives us.
                                        </p>
